sub_title: Editor, content manager, cultural heritage professional
summary:
Editor, web editor, content manager, site formula, ux research and advice. 

As content manager I advise the 7 boroughs of the municipality of Amsterdam about their online presence on Amsterdam.nl. Informing and serving the Amsterdammer is paramount. Through intensive contact with analysis, webmasters, services (call center) and communication my ambition is to bring city and municipality closer together.

projects: [{'title': 'MA thesis', 'date': {'start': {'month': 7, 'day': None, 'year': 2010}, 'end': {'month': 10, 'day': None, 'year': 2010}}, 'description': 'The ornamental painting of residential interiors in Bukhara, Uzbekistan, is the subject of great restoration activity. The work is carried out by skilled house owners or in commission. The results vary between conservation work with respect for the previous layers and rigorous reconstructions with a new interpretation on the basis of traditional elements. Alternatively, Bukharian citizens invest in an interior renewal in what they call ‘Euro-Style’. Funds coming in from abroad, milder legislation and ‘a new identity’ are reasons given for the restorations. With a national identity narrative that people do not identify with, house owners have an interest in promoting the narrative of ‘guarding our own culture before it is lost’. This is especially true for the men as they feel responsible for their family lineage which is connected to the care for the house.\nThe research was carried out under supervision of UCL and UNESCO Uzbekistan. In my research I looked at the reasons for the revival of this traditional style and how this relates to the relative short independence of the Uzbek state. Questionnaires were used to inquire about the attitude towards the traditional cultural heritage and the choice  made regarding the decoration (conservation, reconstruction or destruction) with different generations and gender. \nSummary: www.grad.ucl.ac.uk/comp/2010-2011/research/gallery/index.pht?entryID=11', 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Anna', 'last_name': 'Ietswaart', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Editor, content manager, cultural heritage professional'}, {'type': 'nonStandardizedContributor', 'first_name': None, 'last_name': None, 'name': 'supervised by', 'headline': None}, {'type': 'nonStandardizedContributor', 'first_name': None, 'last_name': None, 'name': 'prof. dr.
